- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with a matrix that depends linearly on some parameters, which is a common setting in systems and control theory. 
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): If none of the above categories fit well, cs.OH can be a catch-all category for papers that do not fit into any specific sub-category.
